						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">jayminer wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I have no idea if any games actually did this.<br /></div>In the thread I linked,<br /><div class="quotetitle">Denine wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">For example, the following games changes palette for status bar:<br />-Wizard &amp; Warriors.<br />-Fantastic Adventurers of Dizzy.<br />-Dizzy the adventurer.<br />-Tom and Jerry.<br /></div><br />I should probably explicitly mention that the &quot;palette entries&quot; I was referring include the normally unusable slots at $3Fx4, $3Fx8, $3FxC, so writing from $3F0D-$3F12 would be 6 visible colors, but writing from $3F01-$3F06 would only be 5. And writing from $3F01-$3F12 would change 15.</div>

